FBIS3-35210 "drnes035_p_94004" FBIS-NES-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Hekmatyar Faction Not To Lift Kabul Blockade LD2202111394 Tripoli JANA in English 0806 GMT 22 Feb 94 LD2202111394 Tripoli JANA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] An-Nawar [Feb] 22, JAMAHIRIYAH NEWS AGENCY -- The faction of Golboddin Hekmatyar which presently surrounds the Afghanistan capital Kabul has announced that it will not lift its blockade which denies the city any relief supplies. The faction was able to intensify its blockade within the pattern of stuggle for power between what were once called mojahedin and later became political rivals whose conflict is systematically destroying the country.
